data.description: Immerse yourself in the charm of this meticulously crafted like-new construction! The floorplan unfolds with a main-level master bedroom and two additional bedrooms sharing a Jack and Jill bathroom. The open-concept living area features cathedral beamed ceilings, and the kitchen is a culinary haven with granite countertops, a sizable island, stylish tile backsplash, ample cabinet space, and a pantry. Gorgeous hardwood floors grace the main level. Upstairs, discover a versatile bonus room, a fourth bedroom, and an open loft area that can be converted to a sixth bedroom or remain a multifunctional space. The covered back patio offers a private retreat overlooking the large, level lot. The versatility and quality craftsmanship shine throughout this home. Welcome Home!
